            . I am a constable. This paper was delivered to me; the prisoner said another boy gave it to him, and agreed to meet him in Queen-street.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I stood in Thames-street; a young lad with two reams of paper under his arm, asked if I had any work - I said No; he said he would give 6d. to carry it to King-street - he ran round the next turning.</p>
